	<message key="plugins.generic.reviewerindex.displayName">Reviewer Index</message>
	<message key="plugins.generic.reviewerindex.description">This plugin compiles a list of reviewers who have completed at least one review for the journal since [YYYY] [MM] [DD]. This list may be used with some layout modification for publication in the last (or first) issue of each volume, as a way to acknowledge reviewers.</message>
	<message key="plugin.generic.reviewerindex.introduction">Select display fields, sort orders, the start and the end dates for the duration you like to have the report. Then click List Reviewers and Save button, to see the list of reviewers for that period of time who have at least one review completed. In addition a link will be appended to about page in Other section, which will publicly display the reviewer index based on your saved settings. </message>

